Module	Description
Search Engine	Queries multiple news APIs + web scraping (with permission)
Reliability Scoring	Uses domain reputation lists (e.g., NewsGuard, MediaBiasFactCheck)
Dual Result Display	Reliable results main view; unreliable in a dropdown
Source Attribution	Every article shows source name, URL, date, bias rating (if available)
Download	Export current result set as Markdown or PDF
Home Page	Default view: trending topics, saved searches, bookmarks
