To search "all over the internet" reliably, you need multiple API keys:

Service	Free Tier	Sign-up Link
NewsAPI.org	100 requests/day	newsapi.org
GNews	100 requests/day	gnews.io
TheNewsAPI	Unlimited*	thenewsapi.com
NewsData.io	200 requests/day	newsdata.io
DuckDuckGo	Free (no key)	-
Tip: Implement automatic failover - if one API fails or hits limit, try the next one .

