9. Challenges & Solutions
Challenge	Solution
Rate limits on free APIs	Use 3-5 APIs with automatic switching
Reliability database accuracy	Start with 200 domains, allow user reports, update weekly
Duplicate articles across APIs	Hash + compare by URL and title
Slow search (multiple APIs)	Parallel requests with Promise.all(), timeout after 5 seconds
"Unreliable" labeling concerns	Always show source name + badge; let users decide
